  "original_title": "\u2018\u0da7\u0ddd\u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca\u2019 \u0d89\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2 \u2018\u0d87\u0db4\u0dca\u0d91\u0d9a\u2018 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The 'token' is over, the 'app' is working",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kumara Rajapaksa, President of the Gas Station Owners Association, said today (19) morning that all the 'tokens' previously given to obtain fuel are invalid and from tomorrow (21) fuel will be issued only according to the last digit of the vehicle's registration number according to the 'National Fuel Licence'.",
        "Mr. Kumara Rajapaksa, President of the Petrol Station Owners' Association, said this at a press conference currently being held in Colombo."
      ],
